  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="Verify local build exists + freshness">
      Confirm `src/solutions/WorkspaceLayoutWizard/dist/sprk_workspacelayoutwizard.html` exists and is newer than the task 032/033 source changes (commit timestamps). If stale, run `cd src/solutions/WorkspaceLayoutWizard && npm run build`.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Read existing Deploy-WizardCodePages.ps1 structure">
      Read `scripts/Deploy-WizardCodePages.ps1` lines 41-58 (the `$webResources` array). Understand the entry shape (Name / DisplayName / Type / Path).
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="Add sprk_workspacelayoutwizard to Deploy-WizardCodePages.ps1">
      Append to the `$webResources` array:
      ```
      @{
          Name = 'sprk_workspacelayoutwizard';
          DisplayName = 'Workspace Layout Wizard';
          Type = 1;  # HTML
          Path = 'src\solutions\WorkspaceLayoutWizard\dist\sprk_workspacelayoutwizard.html';
      }
      ```
      Match the exact formatting + ordering convention used by sibling entries.
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Deploy via updated Deploy-WizardCodePages.ps1">
      Run `scripts/Deploy-WizardCodePages.ps1` (no parameters — defaults to spaarkedev1.crm.dynamics.com). Stream output. Confirm `sprk_workspacelayoutwizard` upload succeeds + customizations published.
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Update deploy memo">
      Append a section to `projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r3/notes/deploys/2026-05-20-deploy.md` documenting this supplemental deploy:
      - What was deployed (sprk_workspacelayoutwizard, build hash if available)
      - Deploy timestamp
      - Reason (Bug 3 fix; smoke feedback)
      - Script change committed (Deploy-WizardCodePages.ps1 now includes this wizard)
    </step>
    <step order="6" name="Update task status + TASK-INDEX">
      Update task 066 POML → completed. Update TASK-INDEX row 066 → ✅.
    </step>
  </steps>

